---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Contribute" description="How to contribute to forHumanity.art - an artist collective building open tools for reflection, healing, and growth.">
  <section class="contribute-hero py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="text-center">Contribute</h1>
      <p class="text-center tagline">
        Join us in building open tools for reflection, healing, and growth.
      </p>
      
      <div class="contribute-content">
        <div class="contribute-intro">
          <p>
            forHumanity.art is an open collective, and we welcome contributions from anyone 
            who shares our values. Whether you're a developer, designer, writer, or just 
            someone who cares about building more humane technology, there's a place for 
            you here.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            We believe that the best tools are built by diverse communities with a shared 
            vision. By contributing to forHumanity.art, you're helping to create a more 
            reflective, intentional, and humane technological future.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="ways-to-contribute">
          <h2>Ways to Contribute</h2>
            
            <div class="contribute-card">
              <h3>Support</h3>
              <p>
                Help us sustain our work through financial contributions. As a non-profit, 
                donation-supported collective, we rely on community support to continue 
                building open tools for reflection, healing, and growth.
              </p>
              <p><em>Donation options coming soon</em></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="getting-started">
          <h2>Getting Started</h2>
          
          <ol>
            <li>
              <strong>Explore our projects:</strong> Visit our <a href="/projects">Projects page</a> 
              to learn about what we're working on.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Join our GitHub organization:</strong> Check out our 
              <a href="https://github.com/forhumanity-org">GitHub repositories</a> and look for 
              issues labeled "good first issue" to get started.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Reach out:</strong> Contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@forhumanity.art">hello@forhumanity.art</a> 
              to introduce yourself and let us know how you'd like to contribute.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Follow our contribution guidelines:</strong> Each project has its own 
              contribution guidelines in its README file. Please review these before contributing.
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>
        
        <div class="community-channels">
          <h2>Community Channels</h2>
          <p>
            We're in the process of setting up community channels for discussion and collaboration. 
            In the meantime, you can reach us via email or GitHub.
          </p>
          <p><em>Community channels coming soon</em></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="code-of-conduct">
          <h2>Code of Conduct</h2>
          <p>
            We're committed to providing a welcoming and inclusive environment for all contributors. 
            We expect all participants to adhere to our code of conduct, which promotes respect, 
            empathy, and collaboration.
          </p>
          <p><em>Full code of conduct coming soon</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-12);
  }
  
  .contribute-content {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .contribute-intro {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }
  
  .ways-to-contribute {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }
  
  .contribute-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .contribute-card {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  
  .contribute-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }
  
  .contribute-card p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .contribute-card a {
    margin-top: auto;
  }
  
  .getting-started {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }
  
  .getting-started ol {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
    padding-left: var(--space-8);
  }
  
  .getting-started li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  
  .community-channels, .code-of-conduct {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .contribute-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
